# Claude Code harness — per-machine, never committed
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/.session-changes.txt

# Node
node_modules/
package-lock.json

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Eval / audit artifacts — regenerable outputs only; the canonical reports stay tracked.
docs/audit/baseline-metrics.md
docs/audit/baseline-metrics.json
docs/audit/skill-eval-report.md
docs/audit/eval-acceptance-*.md
docs/audits/*
!docs/audits/.gitkeep

# Skill-triggering harness — per-run logs (timestamped, large stream-json transcripts)
tests/skill-triggering/logs/

# Graphify build output — costly + per-machine; rebuild via `graphify .` on demand
graphify-out/

# Adopter-project artifacts (these live in the adopter repo, never in the plugin repo).
# Anchored to repo root (leading slash) — without it, Windows case-insensitive matching would
# accidentally block skills/golden-dataset/ (the skill, lowercase) and similar.
/HYPOTHESIS.md
/RESPONSIBILITY-MAP.md
/FEEDBACK-LOG.md
/MODEL-UPGRADE-LOG.md
/OBSERVABILITY.md
/COST-BUDGET.md
/GOLDEN-DATASET/
/EVAL-SUITE/
